\newlabel{tab:h2o_decomp}{{3}{9}{H2O+ decomposition on \texttt {gravity\_soft\_ceiling} (3 seeds, mean shown; $50$k real-env steps except ``offline-only'' which uses D4RL medium-replay + $1024$-step sim warm-up). Offline-only is a clear lower bound; full H2O+ ($r=1.0$) improves dramatically with more offline data; pure online SAC falls well short of both H2O+ and our MC-WM.\relax }{table.caption.25}{}}
